               <p>Second Middlesex Jury - before Mr. Justice James Parke.</p>
               <p>249. 
               <persName id="t18300114-16-defend244" type="defendantName">
                  HENRY TURNER 
                  HARRINGTON
               <interp inst="t18300114-16-defend244" type="surname" value="HARRINGTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300114-16-defend244" type="given" value="HENRY TURNER"></interp>
